title: Here Are The Dos And Don'ts Of Atlanta Pride Weekend
description:
We have waited two years to be a part of one of the best events in the city of Atlanta, pride weekend! You'll catch us in the parade, and we can't wait to see you all. But first, our producer Keity and social media producer Rebecca created a list of dos and don'ts you need to know for the weekend.
